snippet.title: The Midnight Station Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Will you escape The Midnight Station?

http://studio-anjin.co.uk/the-midnight-station/
The Midnight Station is a Surreal Action Adventure RPG, inspired by the ZX Spectrum, OFF, Shpongle and other abstract and often nightmarish mediums. Show us some love by checking the game out in the link above and sharing with your friends, and know that corners can also turn into you...

Please check out these sites as well!
Our Homepage at http://studio-anjin.co.uk/
SpeccyJam at http://www.speccyjam.com/
